  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brace yourself for a candy disaster - Guard your candies against alien goons! With dozens of powerful traps and weapons, make your way through a dangerous planet - Defend thirty-five bases and battle against savage and cunning alien candy thieves!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/f32fa18caba297c4161d9ac0d75f6267.avif?t=1728973743\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>A Wide Variety of Traps</strong></i>: From the good old spikes and cages, to whimsical devices with fun yet deadly effects! Set up human cannons to load up passing goons as cannons, or lay down springboards to toss them into water for sweet environmental kills!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Trap Combo Effects</strong></i>: Make the most of the traps by combining their effects. Pair arrow launchers with flame/poison devices to spice up the arrows, and use fans to change their trajectory.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/8564ff651e86ff23597403aa57765bc5.poster.avif?t=1728973743\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/8564ff651e86ff23597403aa57765bc5.webm?t=1728973743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/8564ff651e86ff23597403aa57765bc5.mp4?t=1728973743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/8599b5d53c6efb13bcaa652afddb4661.avif?t=1728973743\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Grassland, Desert & Iceworld</strong></i>: Each terrain has 10+ bases that will put your defense strategies to test!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>46 Enemies with Unique Abilities</strong></i>: This planet is inhabited by all kinds of clever creatures. Some fly, some swim, and some multiply - Be flexible with your strategies or they will outsmart you!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/6ed71ea5e014c01eeb55c360133969c4.poster.avif?t=1728973743\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/6ed71ea5e014c01eeb55c360133969c4.webm?t=1728973743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/6ed71ea5e014c01eeb55c360133969c4.mp4?t=1728973743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/b95762f7334aed9be53397d615bb3ae0.avif?t=1728973743\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Easy, Challenge & SMASH</strong></i>: 3 levels to pressure test your traps - Experiment with different trap layout and find the best combo for each base! There is also a global leaderboard so claim your throne!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>New Pirate's Loot System</strong></i>: Get random upgrades as you progress through the levels to spice up your arsenal.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/ca4395389e050f02b466b296d5bf0ea3.avif?t=1728973743\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Follow the Genius Scientist Jick</strong></i>: He will tell you all about his crazy trap inventions, take you to the most dangerous corners and the coolest hangouts in space, and teach you the laws of survival. Have fun while slaying creeps!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/62be6245b27d55a05ad301c98b0aa9cf.poster.avif?t=1728973743\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/62be6245b27d55a05ad301c98b0aa9cf.webm?t=1728973743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/62be6245b27d55a05ad301c98b0aa9cf.mp4?t=1728973743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brace yourself for a candy disaster - Guard your candies against alien goons! With dozens of powerful traps and weapons, make your way through a dangerous planet - Defend thirty-five bases and battle against savage and cunning alien candy thieves!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/f32fa18caba297c4161d9ac0d75f6267.avif?t=1728973743\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>A Wide Variety of Traps</strong></i>: From the good old spikes and cages, to whimsical devices with fun yet deadly effects! Set up human cannons to load up passing goons as cannons, or lay down springboards to toss them into water for sweet environmental kills!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Trap Combo Effects</strong></i>: Make the most of the traps by combining their effects. Pair arrow launchers with flame/poison devices to spice up the arrows, and use fans to change their trajectory.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/8564ff651e86ff23597403aa57765bc5.poster.avif?t=1728973743\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/8564ff651e86ff23597403aa57765bc5.webm?t=1728973743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/8564ff651e86ff23597403aa57765bc5.mp4?t=1728973743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/8599b5d53c6efb13bca