akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/ca4395389e050f02b466b296d5bf0ea3.avif?t=1728973743\" width=620 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Follow the Genius Scientist Jick</strong></i>: He will tell you all about his crazy trap inventions, take you to the most dangerous corners and the coolest hangouts in space, and teach you the laws of survival. Have fun while slaying creeps!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/62be6245b27d55a05ad301c98b0aa9cf.poster.avif?t=1728973743\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/62be6245b27d55a05ad301c98b0aa9cf.webm?t=1728973743\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1231460/extras/62be6245b27d55a05ad301c98b0aa9cf.mp4?t=1728973743\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
